gujarati.context:
Here is the translation:

Planted by Bhumi, the earth gave pain; 
The drumbeat of Dhrujiesh's heart gave a thud;
Tugged by the rope, the swing got stuck; 
Spoken to Prabhuji from above came rebuke.

Here is the translation:

Those who have gone back on their word, many have regretted it; 
The one who came and settled there with Vipra, even a donkey has better circumstances than that Vipra's situation.

Here is the translation:

I stayed awake all night, saw Hari laughing; 
After that, we rode the boat when Hari was present, then his companions took a look.
